caption: A dark electronic track with pulsing bass, haunting synth pads, and ethereal processed female vocals. Features industrial textures, glitchy percussion, and an atmospheric build that creates tension and release.
lyrics:
[Intro]

[Verse 1]
Shadows crawling up the wall
I can hear the silence call
Digital dreams in analog skin
Let the darkness pull me in

[Pre-Chorus]
Losing grip on what is real
Tell me what am I supposed to feel

[Chorus]
In the void I find my peace
Where the noise will finally cease
Float away into the black
Never looking back

[Verse 2]
Screens are glowing in the night
Artificial satellite
Connected yet so alone
Searching for a place called home

[Chorus]
In the void I find my peace
Where the noise will finally cease
Float away into the black
Never looking back

[Bridge]

Static fills my mind
Leaving self behind

[Outro]
Float away
Float away
